data.description:
Highest & Best Due Tues 11/7 at 4pm. This beautifully remodeled ranch offers everything you need, with 3 bedrooms and 1 bath.  This home boasts an all-new kitchen and floors, for a fresh and modern feel throughout.

The property sits on a nice deep lot, stretching from street to street. This offers plenty of space for outdoor activities. Additionally, there is a  newer water heater and 2-zone central air and heating system.

Situated in a great neighborhood, this home is conveniently located near Brick beaches and the bay, offering opportunity for  relaxation and recreation. Easy access to Rte. 9 and GSP makes commuting a breeze, allowing you to enjoy all that the area has to offer. Don't miss out on the chance to make this your dream home. Contact us today to schedule a viewing and take the first step towards owning your perfect home in Brick!
